{"tid":1196001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望所有係香港既外資企業可以表達「送中條例」通過後，公司既未來發展如何","createTime":"2019-06-09T17:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T02:12:27.000Z","uid":63626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"935b1e01296553d125cf7e0a736f40be0fc28086","tid":1196001,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:30:39.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，唔少外國公司係香港都有業務<br />\n如果送中條例過左，貴 公司會有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？撤資？定照常營業？<br />\n<br />\n雖然今日有好多人黎遊行，但亦有好多無關注過呢件事既港豬<br />\n假設呢啲外資企業撤走，港豬們會失業、無工返，相信咁樣佢地先會出黎反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日係最後機會<br />\n我亦都唔想見到恆指跌到仆街個陣大家先醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565f50b445fde6ab343a18d63849853060e2c117","tid":1196001,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:42:31.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abddcabf4c10ade5099a412e579372fe40893e0","tid":1196001,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496ef0dffdc195ac02e7932c5a3bd70fcf4415d3","tid":1196001,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad186853340dbcd22f2ebdcf9ecd015400b91f1","tid":1196001,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:11:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51eaae1d4b33a2a600fb84b4ba061f0e00865d2f","tid":1196001,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:46:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d152a88e2eaf77f49af7d25243e2d9741f6554","tid":11